messages.text: You don’t know who this is, do you?
didn’t expect to hear from you so soon ;)
There was someone last week too?
Feel like I’m digging myself a hole.
if you’re not from last night or last wk…
I can’t believe you didn’t keep my #
Never mind. This was obviously a bad idea.
No, no. You can’t just text and then not tell me who you are.
I know, two years ago. Must be hard.
No, but my best friend’s boyfriend did. Remember Becca?
God. I thought maybe you had grown up some.
Ok, Kali. What do you want?
You’re still friends with Andy, right?
The best of friends. We’re even roommates.
I mean, he did get laid off recently. And mostly he stays in his room...
Do you think he still has feelings for Becca?
Right. If they were still together at their five-year high school reunion…
Then they’d get engaged. They even had matching promise rings.
I tried to tell him high school relationships never last.
I think they still love each other. Do you know what’s coming up?
I feel like you’re up to something.
Do you think Andy still loves Becca?
I’m sure he got rid of it.
Prove it. You said you’re roommates. See if he hid it anywhere.
Don’t you want to see your best friend happy again?
All right. He’s at the laundromat. I guess I could take a quick peek…
;) You don't know the half of it.
Okay, I’m looking around his desk. He’s been working on a novel.
I thought he was a stock analyst.
Rubber bands? Paper clips? Why does he have so many paper clips?
Nothing in the desk. Checking the nightstand.
There’s a copy of Twilight in the drawer :-/
Check his sock drawer. That’s where all guys keep their private stuff.
No. My socks! He’s been stealing my socks!
Sorry. I don’t know where else to look.
All right...shoes, belts...wait - here’s a cigar box...
I think someone’s unlocking the front door.
If he catches me, I’m screwed!
Pictures. Of him and Becca. And…
The ring. He kept the ring. Crap. I hear him.
I put the box back but he found me in his room.
I told him I’d run out of socks ;)
I guess. It was a close call.
It doesn’t mean he loves her.
It means he still has feelings. They’re both so miserable.
What if they’re meant to be together?
What are we supposed to do about it??
Their five year reunion is in two months. If we can get them back together by then…
Don’t you want Andy to be happy?
I can’t believe he kept the ring.
We have to do whatever we can to get them back together.
Whatever. The point is, we have to work together.
Okay. Wait. Doesn’t Becca live in Seattle?
We live in NYC! This is basically impossible!
Andy just came in my room and said a publisher was interested in his novel!!!
He thanked me for sending it????!
I work for a publishing house. It wasn’t hard to get Andy’s e-mail.
I said you sent it with the best intentions ;)
When he flies to Seattle for the meeting I’m going to make sure he “accidentally” runs into Becca.
I hope you know what you’re doing.
Of course. We have nothing to lose. :oD
